('galpani2','Gals Panic II (Asia)',2,true,false,true,false,'This game didn''t actually label the button and in all the docs it''s referred to as button 1, however it is clear what this button does.  I labeled it ''cut'' to avoid confusion as ''button 1'' may seem like a parsing error to the average viewer.  Also take note that the pcb has inputs for three physical buttons and they are emulated in mame, but only the first is used.',ARRAY[]::TEXT[]),
